Description: Picshare is a location-based photo app that allows one to share photos with friends.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Instant and effortless sharing of photos and videos. Picshare is a location-based photo and video app that allows you to instantly and effortlessly share photos and videos with friends and others nearby, simply with the push of a button! Take a photo or video with picshare, and the app automatically shares it with other nearby users - no texting, emailing, or networking required. Picshare's proprietary technology takes away all the work required of sharing. Simply open the app and take a photo or shoot a video, as you would your camera, and you're done! Photos and videos taken within 500 meters are gathered in your personal picshare stream, instantly generating an album of your day's events. Want to download a few for safe keeping ? go for it ! Want to upload to Facebook, Instagram or Twitter? Picshare allows you to do that as well. All you have to do is point and click, and picshare does the rest of the work for you. Of course, how much you share is up to you. Picshare allows you to select who exactly can see your photos and videos, be it your Facebook friends or everyone nearby. So if you're at a private party, you can keep it private and share only with your closest friends; if you're at a football game, feel free to share it with everyone in the stadium. No matter how big or small, you're able to create a record of your memories with no effort at all and control who you share with. * Automatically share photos and videos with friends and other users within 500 meters * Download any photos and videos shared to store memories of your favorite events. * View your stream to see all photos and videos taken nearby - an album created without any work from you. * Adjust your privacy settings to decide who exactly can see your photos and videos. * See how many people have downloaded your photos and videos. * Connect with Facebook, Twitter, and email to share your photos and videos with the world. Picshare is the first-of-its-kind, designed to allow you to share experiences without the effort required by texts, emails, and social networks.  Andriod & Windows versions coming soon.............

Full Description: Information technology and telecommunications are playing an ever larger role in our everyday lives. Online firms, like Google, Apple, Microsoft, Facebook and Yahoo! (“GAMFY”) have become household brands. What makes these Internet and cloud firms work? The answer is data centers. These firms would not operate without physical buildings in which to place the computers that deliver content to consumers. As you might imagine, computers are not the typical large-scale occupant of a building, and computers can be exceedingly demanding. These demands take the form of electrical power on the scale of small cities, cooling that dwarfs large-scale frozen food manufacturing, and many, many telecom lines…the kind of telecom lines that cross oceans and feed entire countries. It may not be in front of your face, but we are witnessing the birth of a new class of real estate specifically designed to support the Internet Era. ‘Wired’ Real Estate. Wired Real Estate Group Inc. (“WiredRE”) is the nation’s leading independent cloud, colocation and data center advisory firm. WiredRE use their proprietary methodology to advise enterprises on data center planning, brokerage and finance. The firms unique and proprietary methodology has enabled WiredRE to advise two of the top three global telecom firms and over half of the nation’s top and most admired banks in transactions up to $100 million. Nationally, the firm represents nearly 1 M square feet of colocation and data centers for lease and sale, and in 2014 the company became the #1 independent listing agent in the UK. As an extension of its brokerage practice, WiredRE operate and maintain a free global colocation and data center list. One can search, qualify and map data centers down to the street level. Description: Virsona, Inc. is a new social media service that lets users create online virtual personas that come to life via realistic, real-time
Headquarters Regions: Greater Miami Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Virsona, Inc. is a new social media service that lets users create online virtual personas that "come to life" via realistic, real-time chat, allowing people to build relationships with individuals and brands they never thought possible.  Conversations are at the foundation of every relationship and relationships are what drive engagement and loyalty to people and brands. Virsona is redefining how people can connect with one another to strengthen relationships between friends, family, characters or brands. Virsona enables users to create virtual personas, or Virsonas, of real-life, fictional or historical figures, living or dead, who through an online chat format independently and intuitively remember, react and respond just like the person or brand they were designed to emulate. The Virsonas are powered by the company's innovative, patent-pending artificial intelligence technology, which gives the service its human-like chat capabilities. Users create Virsonas by building online life archives of facts, letters, journals, memories and photos and then invite family and friends to access and interact with their Virsona and its content. The more information that is added to a Virsona the more accurate and interactive that Virsona will be. There are two different types of Virsonas. The first is your own Personal Virsona and the second is Community Virsonas. You can interact with Community Virsonas simply by clicking on the picture and chatting. To add information to an existing Community Virsona or participate in building a new one, you must create an account and log in.    A Personal Virsona allows users to establish a digital immortality by creating and building an interactive legacy and archive for people to communicate with and access for generations to come.  With a Personal Virsona based on your own life experiences, you can "live" forever online.  The first step in creating your own Personal Virsona is by establishing a free account and login at www.virsona.com. Once you create your free account, you can start populating your Virsona with your life memories. The more memories and thoughts you add to your Virsona the more your Virsona will remember, reason and react just like you.   Consumers populate their Virsonas thru a chat box. The conversation looks much like an Instant Messaging, or Text Messaging chat. Simply click on the chat box and type away. Consumers can also populate their Virsona with emails, video, photos, etc.  Through regular use of the Virsona, users can "train" their online self to act, "speak" and behave like they would in real life. Personal Virsonas can also be shared with friends and family and can be made private or public.   Virsona is the key to consumers' "immortality."  Note: This is a free service to consumers.
Industry Groups: Information Technology, Internet Services, Media and Entertainment, Messaging and Telecommunications
